    "By faith he forsook <span class=\"place\">Egypt</span>, not fearing the wrath of the king: for he endured, as seeing him who is invisible.",
    "Through faith he kept the passover, and the sprinkling of blood, lest he that destroyed the firstborn should touch them.",
    "By faith they passed through the Red sea as by dry land: which the Egyptians assaying to do were drowned.",
    "By faith the walls of <span class=\"place\">Jericho</span> fell down, after they were compassed about seven days.",
