    "And what shall I more say? for the time would fail me to tell of Gedeon, and of <span class=\"person\">Barak</span>, and of <span class=\"person\">Samson</span>, and of <span class=\"person\">Jephthae</span>; of <span class=\"person\">David</span> also, and <span class=\"person\">Samuel</span>, and of the prophets:",
